16 SECTION 1. BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF MARYLAND,
17 That the Laws of Maryland read as follows:
18 Article – Courts and Judicial Proceedings
19 3–2502.
20 (a) A firearm industry member may not knowingly create, maintain, or contribute
21 to harm to the public through the sale, manufacture, distribution, importation, or
22 marketing of a firearm–related product by engaging in conduct that is:
23 (1) Unlawful; or
